<a name="NYSE:CPQ"></a><a href="http://www.hoovers.com/cgi-bin/brand_worth_mlist.cgi?mode=full&index_code=10381"><img src="/imgs/graph.gif" border=0><b>Compaq Computer</b></a>  (NYSE: CPQ)  $65<br>
* Strong new-product availability<br>
* Beneficiary of Windows NT 4.0 and Pentium Pro upgrade cycles<br>
