* Rising debt
* Intense competition
* Deteriorating balance sheet<p>Transaction Network Srvs. (Nasdaq: TNSI) $13
* Sharply falling prices
* Intense competition
* Rising capital expenditures <p><a name="NASD:XPED"></a><a href="http://www.hoovers.com/cgi-bin/brand_worth_mlist.cgi?mode=full&index_code=16836"><img src="/imgs/graph.gif" border=0><b>Xpedite Systems</b></a> (Nasdaq: XPED) $13
* Key management departure
* Bad acquisition 
* Competition from Internet<p><p><p>
KEYWORDS: Stock Investing Strategies

					</font>
					<p>
		
		
		
