					<p>

<font size=+1><b>Company Index</b><br>
</font>						<a href="#NYSE:ASH">Ashland Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:LLTC">Linear Technology Corporation</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:MO">Philip Morris Companies Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:ZE">Zenith Electronics Corporation</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:AMD">Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#ASE:FRX">Forest Laboratories </a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:GLX">Glaxo Wellcome plc</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:MU">Micron Technology, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:CALL">Nextel Communications, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:VJET">ValuJet, Inc.</a><br>

					<p>

					<p>
	
		
</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td width=390>
	
