						<a href="#NYSE:MRK">Merck & Co., Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:MO">Philip Morris Companies Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:F">Ford Motor Company</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:WHR">Whirlpool Corporation</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:CAT">Caterpillar Inc.</a><br>

