<DOCHDR>
http://www.worth.com:80/articles/Z9510N02.html 204.141.48.165 19970209101522 text/html 8212
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 09 Feb 1997 10:16:10 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
