</font>						<a href="#NASD:MSFT">Microsoft Corporation</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:INTU">Intuit Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:BJS">BJ Services Company</a><br>

					<p>

<font size=+1><b>Mutual Fund Index</b><br>
</font>						<a href="#FUND:MERFX">Merger Fund</a><br>

