<DOCOLDNO>IA031-000660-B031-293</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.worth.com:80/articles/Z9701I02.html 204.141.48.165 19970209105931 text/html 10840
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 09 Feb 1997 10:59:48 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
Content-type: text/html
