						This basic yet effective model is a good starting point for any investor. It's specifically designed for a 45-year-old who plans to remain invested for at least 20 years. It offers moderate risk and can be built with mutual funds, stocks, or a combination of both.<p>
30%     Large-Cap Value 
22%     Global 
20%     Large-Cap Growth
15%     Small-Cap Value
13%     Small-Cap Growth
