<DOCNO>WT14-B07-242</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA031-000660-B034-235</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.worth.com:80/articles/Z9611F02.html 204.141.48.165 19970209110631 text/html 7983
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
